  "detailed_description": "<strong>Witch Guild Survivor</strong> is a fun horde roguelite game where you play as a witch that must survive from the monsters using your poweful spells! Collect white orbs and upgrade your magic spells. Choose a combination of various elements to generate synergies between them in each run. Let's have some fun in this horde survival game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163230/extras/fad45f20f7e5cd467f387351a0826f51.poster.avif?t=1676502153\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163230/extras/fad45f20f7e5cd467f387351a0826f51.webm?t=1676502153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163230/extras/fad45f20f7e5cd467f387351a0826f51.mp4?t=1676502153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DYNAMIC BUILDS</h2>In this roguelite survival game, you can choose a combination of various elements to generate synergies between them in each run.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163230/extras/917257a213531b73b6cb6710a4390cb2.poster.avif?t=1676502153\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163230/extras/917257a213531b73b6cb6710a4390cb2.webm?t=1676502153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163230/extras/917257a213531b73b6cb6710a4390cb2.mp4?t=1676502153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SELECT YOUR WITCH, WAND AND SPELL</h2>Choose from the witches, wands and spells available in this demo version. Each combination generates a different game experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163230/extras/51f6a18837a272763b09ac53b07e2575.poster.avif?t=1676502153\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163230/extras/51f6a18837a272763b09ac53b07e2575.webm?t=1676502153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163230/extras/51f6a18837a272763b09ac53b07e2575.mp4?t=1676502153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>10 different elements that add 50 improvements and different game experiences<br></li><li>Each upgrade can be upgraded up to level 4 to boost your strategy<br></li><li>Unique Special Attack mechanic<br></li><li>Random quest system<br></li><li>Can be played with or without a mouse<br></li><li>Its a fun horde survival game!!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163230/extras/38be5ccc79581d2f38a5d2907340d62b.poster.avif?t=1676502153\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163230/extras/38be5ccc79581d2f38a5d2907340d62b.webm?t=1676502153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163230/extras/38be5ccc79581d2f38a5d2907340d62b.mp4?t=1676502153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
